Outline¶

  • Adding a title page
  • Selecting a template

Adding a title page¶

a Title page is added by adding to the notebook metadata

"KULeuvenSlides": {
        "title": "test title",
        "subtitle": "test subtitle",
        "authors": "Jan Genoe",
        "location": "Ergens",
        "date": "Vandaag"
    },

Please do not forget to commit changes after adding metadata. (The small v on top of the box).

Selecting a template¶

a Title page is added by adding to the notebook metadata

"KULeuvenSlides": {
        "kuleuven_presentation_style": "1425"
    },

These slides are using the "1425" template. The following templates are available:

  • Sedes
  • Normal
  • 1425 (the key)

Please do not forget to commit changes after adding metadata. (The small v on top of the box).
